{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Ezk|28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","chapter":28,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":1,"text":"The word of the Lord came to me:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":2,"text":"“Son of man, say to the ruler of Tyre, ‘This is what the Lord God says: Your heart is proud, and you have said, “I am a god; I sit in the seat of gods in the heart of the sea.” Yet you are a man and not a god, though you have regarded your heart as that of a god.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":3,"text":"Yes, you are wiser than Daniel; no secret is hidden from you!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":4,"text":"By your wisdom and understanding you have acquired wealth for yourself. You have acquired gold and silver for your treasuries.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":5,"text":"By your great skill in trading you have increased your wealth, but your heart has become proud because of your wealth.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":6,"text":"“ ‘Therefore, this is what the Lord God says: Because you regard your heart as that of a god,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":7,"text":"I am about to bring strangers against you, ruthless men from the nations. They will draw their swords against your magnificent wisdom and will pierce your splendor.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":8,"text":"They will bring you down to the Pit, and you will die a violent death in the heart of the sea.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":9,"text":"Will you still say, “I am a god,” in the presence of those who slay you? Yet you will be only a man, not a god, in the hands of those who kill you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":10,"text":"You will die the death of the uncircumcised at the hands of strangers. For I have spoken.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":11,"text":"The word of the Lord came to me:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":12,"text":"“Son of man, lament for the king of Tyre and say to him, ‘This is what the Lord God says: You were the seal of perfection, full of wisdom and perfect in beauty.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":13,"text":"You were in Eden, the garden of God. Every kind of precious stone covered you: carnelian, topaz, and diamond, beryl, onyx, and jasper, lapis lazuli, turquoise and emerald. Your mountings and settings were crafted in gold; they were prepared on the day you were created.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":14,"text":"You were an anointed guardian cherub, for I had appointed you. You were on the holy mountain of God; you walked among the fiery stones.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":15,"text":"From the day you were created you were blameless in your ways until wickedness was found in you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":16,"text":"Through the abundance of your trade, you were filled with violence, and you sinned. So I expelled you in disgrace from the mountain of God, and banished you, guardian cherub, from among the fiery stones.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":17,"text":"Your heart became proud because of your beauty; For the sake of your splendor you corrupted your wisdom. So I threw you down to the ground; I made you a spectacle before kings.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":18,"text":"You profaned your sanctuaries by the magnitude of your iniquities in your dishonest trade. So I made fire come from within you, and it consumed you. I reduced you to ashes on the ground in the sight of everyone watching you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":19,"text":"All those who know you among the peoples are appalled at you. You have become an object of horror and will never exist again.’”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":20,"text":"The word of the Lord came to me:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":21,"text":"“Son of man, face Sidon and prophesy against it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":22,"text":"You are to say, ‘This is what the Lord God says: Look! I am against you, Sidon, and I will display my glory within you. They will know that I am the Lord when I execute judgments against her and demonstrate my holiness through her.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":23,"text":"I will send a plague against her and bloodshed in her streets; the slain will fall within her, while the sword is against her on every side. Then they will know that I am the Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":24,"text":"“ ‘The house of Israel will no longer be hurt by prickly briers or painful thorns from all their neighbors who treat them with contempt. Then they will know that I am the Lord God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":25,"text":"“ ‘This is what the Lord God says: When I gather the house of Israel from the peoples where they are scattered, I will demonstrate my holiness through them in the sight of the nations, and they will live in their own land, which I gave to my servant Jacob.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","bookOrder":25,"chapter":28,"verse":26,"text":"They will live there securely, build houses, and plant vineyards. They will live securely when I execute judgments against all their neighbors who treat them with contempt. Then they will know that I am the Lord their God.’”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Ezk","chapter":28,"paragraphStarts":[1,6,7,8,9,10,11,13,14,15,16,17,18,19,20,23,24,25],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"The Fall of Tyre’s Ruler"},{"beforeVerse":11,"text":"A Lament for Tyre’s King"},{"beforeVerse":20,"text":"A Prophecy against Sidon"}],"poetryBlocks":[{"beforeVerse":7,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":8,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":9,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":10,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":13,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":14,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":15,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":16,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":17,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":18,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":19,"level":1},{"beforeVerse":23,"level":1}],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The word of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" came to me: "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Son of man, say to the ruler of Tyre, ‘This is what the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: Your "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit Because your"},{"kind":"text","text":" heart is proud, and you have said, “I am a god; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 14:14","book":"Isa","chapter":14,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 12:22–23","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 2:4","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" I sit in the seat of gods in the heart of the sea.” Yet you are a man and not a god, though you have regarded your heart as that of a god. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 14:14","book":"Isa","chapter":14,"verse":14},{"label":"Ac 12:22–23","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":22},{"label":"2Th 2:4","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit Because your"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yes, you are wiser than Daniel; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 1:20","book":"Dan","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 2:20–23","book":"Dan","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 2:28","book":"Dan","chapter":2,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 5:11–12","book":"Dan","chapter":5,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" no secret is hidden from you! "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dn 1:20","book":"Dan","chapter":1,"verse":20},{"label":"Dn 2:20–23","book":"Dan","chapter":2,"verse":20},{"label":"Dn 2:28","book":"Dan","chapter":2,"verse":28},{"label":"Dn 5:11–12","book":"Dan","chapter":5,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"By your wisdom and understanding you have acquired wealth for yourself. You have acquired gold and silver for your treasuries. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 27:33","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":33,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 9:2","book":"Zec","chapter":9,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 27:33","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":33},{"label":"Zch 9:2","book":"Zec","chapter":9,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"By your great skill in trading you have increased your wealth, but your heart has become proud because of your wealth."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“ ‘Therefore, this is what the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Because you regard your heart as that of a god,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am about to bring strangers against you,"},{"kind":"text","text":" ruthless men from the nations."},{"kind":"text","text":" They will draw their swords"},{"kind":"text","text":" against your magnificent wisdom"},{"kind":"text","text":" and will pierce your splendor. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 30:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 31:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 32:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":32,"verse":12,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 30:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":11},{"label":"Ezk 31:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":12},{"label":"Ezk 32:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":32,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will bring you down to the Pit, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 26:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and you will die a violent death"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the heart of the sea."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 26:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Will you still say, “I am a god,”"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the presence of those who slay "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, LXX, Syr, Vg; other Hb mss read of the one who kills"},{"kind":"text","text":" you?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Yet you will be only a man, not a god,"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the hands of those who kill you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, LXX, Syr, Vg; other Hb mss read of the one who kills"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You will die the death of the uncircumcised "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 31:18","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 32:30","book":"Ezk","chapter":32,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" at the hands of strangers. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 30:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" For I have spoken."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 31:18","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":18},{"label":"Ezk 32:30","book":"Ezk","chapter":32,"verse":30},{"label":"Ezk 30:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The word of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" came to me: "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Son of man, lament "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 27:2","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the king of Tyre and say to him, ‘This is what the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says:"},{"kind":"text","text":" You were the seal "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or sealer"},{"kind":"text","text":" of perfection, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Hb obscure"},{"kind":"text","text":" full of wisdom and perfect in beauty. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 27:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":3,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 27:2","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":2},{"label":"Ezk 27:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or sealer"},{"marker":2,"text":"Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You were in Eden, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 2:8","book":"Gen","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 31:9","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 31:16","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 31:18","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":18,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 36:35","book":"Ezk","chapter":36,"verse":35,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" the garden of God."},{"kind":"text","text":" Every kind of precious stone covered you:"},{"kind":"text","text":" carnelian, topaz, and diamond, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"},{"kind":"text","text":" beryl, onyx, and jasper,"},{"kind":"text","text":" lapis lazuli, turquoise "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or malachite, or garnet"},{"kind":"text","text":" and emerald. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or beryl"},{"kind":"text","text":" Your mountings and settings were crafted in gold; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 39:10–13","book":"Exo","chapter":39,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" they were prepared on the day you were created."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 2:8","book":"Gen","chapter":2,"verse":8},{"label":"Ezk 31:9","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":9},{"label":"Ezk 31:16","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":16},{"label":"Ezk 31:18","book":"Ezk","chapter":31,"verse":18},{"label":"Ezk 36:35","book":"Ezk","chapter":36,"verse":35},{"label":"Ex 39:10–13","book":"Exo","chapter":39,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"},{"marker":1,"text":"Or malachite, or garnet"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or beryl"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You were an anointed guardian cherub, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 25:18–22","book":"Exo","chapter":25,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or With an anointed guardian cherub"},{"kind":"text","text":" I had appointed you."},{"kind":"text","text":" You were on the holy mountain of God;"},{"kind":"text","text":" you walked among the fiery stones."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 25:18–22","book":"Exo","chapter":25,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or With an anointed guardian cherub"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From the day you were created"},{"kind":"text","text":" you were blameless in your ways"},{"kind":"text","text":" until wickedness was found in you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Through the abundance of your trade,"},{"kind":"text","text":" you were filled with violence, and you sinned."},{"kind":"text","text":" So I expelled you in disgrace"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the mountain of God,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and banished you, guardian cherub, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or and the guardian cherub banished you"},{"kind":"text","text":" from among the fiery stones."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or and the guardian cherub banished you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Your heart became proud because of your beauty; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 28:2","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" For the sake of your splendor"},{"kind":"text","text":" you corrupted your wisdom."},{"kind":"text","text":" So I threw you down to the ground; "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or earth"},{"kind":"text","text":" I made you a spectacle before kings."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 28:2","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or earth"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You profaned your sanctuaries"},{"kind":"text","text":" by the magnitude of your iniquities"},{"kind":"text","text":" in your dishonest trade."},{"kind":"text","text":" So I made fire come from within you,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and it consumed you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 19:14","book":"Ezk","chapter":19,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" I reduced you to ashes on the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the sight of everyone watching you."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 19:14","book":"Ezk","chapter":19,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"All those who know you among the peoples"},{"kind":"text","text":" are appalled at you."},{"kind":"text","text":" You have become an object of horror"},{"kind":"text","text":" and will never exist again.’” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 26:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 27:36","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":36,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 26:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":21},{"label":"Ezk 27:36","book":"Ezk","chapter":27,"verse":36}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The word of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" came to me: "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Son of man, face Sidon "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 10:19","book":"Gen","chapter":10,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 23:2","book":"Isa","chapter":23,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jl 3:4","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and prophesy against it. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 10:19","book":"Gen","chapter":10,"verse":19},{"label":"Is 23:2","book":"Isa","chapter":23,"verse":2},{"label":"Jl 3:4","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are to say, ‘This is what the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Look! I am against you, Sidon, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 26:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 9:2","book":"Zec","chapter":9,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:22","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and I will display my glory within you."},{"kind":"text","text":" They will know that I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" when I execute judgments against her "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 30:19","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and demonstrate my holiness through her."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 26:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":3},{"label":"Zch 9:2","book":"Zec","chapter":9,"verse":2},{"label":"Mt 11:22","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":22},{"label":"Ezk 30:19","book":"Ezk","chapter":30,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will send a plague against her "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 38:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":38,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and bloodshed in her streets;"},{"kind":"text","text":" the slain will fall within her,"},{"kind":"text","text":" while the sword is against her "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or within her by the sword"},{"kind":"text","text":" on every side."},{"kind":"text","text":" Then they will know that I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 38:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":38,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or within her by the sword"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“ ‘The house of Israel will no longer be hurt by "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit longer have"},{"kind":"text","text":" prickly briers or painful thorns "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 33:55","book":"Num","chapter":33,"verse":55,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" from all their neighbors who treat them with contempt. Then they will know that I am the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 33:55","book":"Num","chapter":33,"verse":55}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit longer have"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“ ‘This is what the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: When I gather the house of Israel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 106:47","book":"Psa","chapter":106,"verse":47,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 20:41","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":41,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:13","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the peoples where they are scattered, I will demonstrate my holiness through them in the sight of the nations, and they will live in their own land, which I gave to my servant Jacob. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 106:47","book":"Psa","chapter":106,"verse":47},{"label":"Ezk 20:41","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":41},{"label":"Ezk 34:13","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Ezk:28:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will live there securely, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:6","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:28","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 38:8","book":"Ezk","chapter":38,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" build houses, and plant vineyards. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:15","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":15,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 11:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":11,"verse":3,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" They will live securely when I execute judgments "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 25:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":25,"verse":11,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" against all their neighbors who treat them with contempt. Then they will know that I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" their God.’”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 23:6","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":6},{"label":"Ezk 34:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":25},{"label":"Ezk 34:28","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":28},{"label":"Ezk 38:8","book":"Ezk","chapter":38,"verse":8},{"label":"Jr 32:15","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":15},{"label":"Ezk 11:3","book":"Ezk","chapter":11,"verse":3},{"label":"Ezk 25:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":25,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279584282}